            <div class="col-lg-6 content order-last  order-lg-first">
                <h3>About Us</h3>
                <p>
                    We are a team who is well aware of the cyber threats, threat actors, the risks online and how much damage a cyber attack can cause. We want to spread the awareness and help people protect themselves from these threats. Because we believe that no company or initiative can protect all the people from cyber attacks since there are infinitely many, so the best solution to this problem is everyone protecting one person,  themselves.
                </p>
