                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                        <i class="mt-4 fa-solid fa-people-group"></i>
                        <div>
                            <h5>Our Team</h5>
                            <p>Our team is composed of qualified and experienced people in the field of cyber security. We continuously improve the services we provide and increase the numbers of cyber attack simulations - vulnerability tests - that we have on our website.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                        <i class="bi bi-broadcast"></i>
                        <div>
                            <h5>Our Goal</h5>
                            <p>What we focus on currently is to raise, promote and spread awareness all around the world about cyber security. Help us spread the word.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section><!-- End About Us Section -->
